'''Richard McGonagle''' born [[October 22]], [[1940s#1946|1946]]) is an [[Wikipedia:America|American]] voice actor who provided the voices of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Grievous/Legends|Grievous]], [[Kit Fisto/Legends|Kit Fisto]], [[Orvos]], and [[Harvos]] in [[Clone Wars: Season Three|Season Three]] of the ''[[Star Wars: Clone Wars]]'' cartoon. He also provided the voice of a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] soldier for the computer game ''[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron II: Rogue Leader]]''.

He also had a bit part in the [[Lucasfilm]] cult/camp film, [[Wikipedia:Howard the Duck (film)|''Howard the Duck'']].

